{"parents": [], "prev": {"link": "../analytics/reference/", "title": "Reference"}, "next": {"link": "guides/emails/design_email/", "title": "Designing an Email"}, "title": "Automation", "meta": null, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"automation\">\n<h1>Automation<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#automation\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<p>The automation app lets users craft custom workflows for users that automate\nsome portion of the user\u2019s journey. Triggered by some external action (e.g.\nresponding to a form, clicking a link in an email, etc), users are enrolled in\na workflow and then passed through a series of steps that either alter their\ncustomer record or send some sort of communication.</p>\n<div class=\"toctree-wrapper compound\">\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/design_email/\">Designing an Email</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_text_block/\">Text Email Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_divider_block/\">Divider Email Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_image_block/\">Image Email Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_button_block/\">Button Email Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_preference_block/\">Preferences Email Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_social_share_block/\">Social Share Email Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_social_follow_block/\">Social Follow Email Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\"><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"guides/emails/email_video_block/\">Video Email Block</a></li>\n<li class=\"toctree-l1\">